{%- comment -%}
  PFD1 — Advertorial listicle for WLP-1. Top-of-funnel, Meta cold paid traffic.
  Hook: "5 Things We're Sorry About" — consequence-shaped flexes, not benefit-shaped.
  Audience: female 35-55, GLP-1 curious, needle-averse. Editorial feel, soft product reveal at bottom.
  Brand voice: declarative, no em dashes, no exclamation points, ~prefix on weight numbers, * on s/f claims.
  Never reference Ozempic by name. Always "GLP-1 injections."
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign hero_img      = section.settings.hero_img      | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/lifestyle-image-1-wlp-1.jpg?v=1775677645'
  assign product_img   = section.settings.product_img   | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_WLP1.png?crop=center&height=1200&v=1774483977&width=1200'
  assign img_1         = section.settings.img_1         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/lifestyle-image-1-wlp-1.jpg?v=1775677645'
  assign img_2         = section.settings.img_2         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_WLP1.png?crop=center&height=1200&v=1774483977&width=1200'
  assign img_3         = section.settings.img_3         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/lifestyle-image-1-wlp-1.jpg?v=1775677645'
  assign img_4         = section.settings.img_4         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/lifestyle-image-1-wlp-1.jpg?v=1775677645'
  assign img_5         = section.settings.img_5         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/lifestyle-image-1-wlp-1.jpg?v=1775677645'
  assign cart_1mo      = section.settings.cart_1mo      | default: '/cart/52472821121313:1?selling_plan=691162546465'
  assign cart_3mo      = section.settings.cart_3mo      | default: '/cart/52472821154081:1?selling_plan=691162579233'
  assign cart_6mo      = section.settings.cart_6mo      | default: '/cart/52472821186849:1?selling_plan=691166544161'
  assign price_1mo_per   = section.settings.price_1mo_per   | default: '$79.20/mo'
  assign price_1mo_was   = section.settings.price_1mo_was   | default: '$99.00'
  assign price_1mo_total = section.settings.price_1mo_total | default: '$79.20 total'
  assign price_1mo_save  = section.settings.price_1mo_save  | default: 'save $19.80'
  assign discount_1mo    = section.settings.discount_1mo    | default: '20'
  assign price_3mo_per   = section.settings.price_3mo_per   | default: '$69.30/mo'
  assign price_3mo_was   = section.settings.price_3mo_was   | default: '$297.00'
  assign price_3mo_total = section.settings.price_3mo_total | default: '$207.90 total'
  assign price_3mo_save  = section.settings.price_3mo_save  | default: 'save $89.10'
  assign discount_3mo    = section.settings.discount_3mo    | default: '30'
  assign price_6mo_per   = section.settings.price_6mo_per   | default: '$64.35/mo'
  assign price_6mo_was   = section.settings.price_6mo_was   | default: '$594.00'
  assign price_6mo_total = section.settings.price_6mo_total | default: '$386.10 total'
  assign price_6mo_save  = section.settings.price_6mo_save  | default: 'save $207.90'
  assign discount_6mo    = section.settings.discount_6mo    | default: '35'
  assign rating        = section.settings.rating        | default: '4.5'
  assign review_count  = section.settings.review_count  | default: '1,200+'
  assign byline        = section.settings.byline        | default: 'By The Absorption Company Editorial'
  assign pub_date      = section.settings.pub_date      | default: 'May 2026'
  assign read_time     = section.settings.read_time     | default: '6 min read'

  comment
    Hero copy. Schema-editable so the H1 can be swapped to message-match each ad creative
    without a code change. HTML allowed in headline/dek so you can italicize the highlight phrase.
  endcomment
  assign kicker_text   = section.settings.kicker_text   | default: 'Read Before You Try GLP-1 Injections'
  assign headline_html = section.settings.headline_html | default: "We're Sorry In Advance: 5 Things Nobody Warned You About <em>WLP-1</em>."
  assign dek_html      = section.settings.dek_html      | default: 'The natural oral GLP-1 support helping women 35 to 55 drop <b>~9 lbs in 4 weeks</b><sup>*</sup>. No needles, no prescription. Here is what nobody warned us about.'
  assign lede_text     = section.settings.lede_text     | default: 'Before you start WLP-1, we owe you five honest warnings about what tends to happen once the weight starts coming off.'
  assign hero_cta_text = section.settings.hero_cta_text | default: 'See WLP-1 plans'

  comment
    Optional asset slots. All render hide-if-empty so the page still works pre-asset.
  endcomment
  assign ugc_video_url     = section.settings.ugc_video_url
  assign ugc_video_poster  = section.settings.ugc_video_poster
