        <figure class="pfd1-secimg">
          <img src="{{ img_2 }}" alt="WLP-1 supplement bottle on a clean countertop." loading="lazy" width="900" height="675">
        </figure>
        <p>Someone leans in at brunch and asks, <em>"are you on the shots?"</em> You say no, but the results look close enough that nobody quite believes you.</p>
        <p>WLP-1 is not an injection. It is two pills a day on the same natural GLP-1 pathway the shots target,<sup>*</sup> plus two more pathways the shots do not touch.</p>
        <p>No needles, no prescription, no monthly trip to a clinic.</p>
        <p>You will get used to explaining it. Or you can stop explaining and let the change in your jeans do the talking.</p>
        <div class="pfd1-sorry__pull">
          <b>Triple-pathway, not single-pathway.</b> Appetite, metabolic rate, and thermogenesis at once.<sup>*</sup>
        </div>
      </section>

